data.description: Beautiful home waiting for it's next family to fulfill their dreams & new memories. Huge fenced in backyard. Basement has a nice gas fireplace to enjoy those winter days & nights. Many upgrades to mention! So come see for yourself before this one is gone. 85 gallon smart water heater. Ceiling fans throughout. Sunroom off the dining area. Home is hardwired for network.  Hardwood flooring. HOA is optional per seller & it is for the community swimming pool & Park area. Park is great for playing basketball, volleyball, football, soccer, BBQ's, birthday parties. This home has the potential to be 5 bedrooms w/flex room down in basement. There is a table that is attached in garage that folds down for that handyman that works in garage & an outdoor sink in backyard. There is also raised garden beds for her to enjoy gardening. Newer Kitchen Appliances included. SQFT based on last listing. Professional measurements & photos coming soon. Seller says Loan is assumable at 4.51% interest with VA
